2024/03/The-Black-Keys@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Black-Keys@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Black-Keys@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Black-Keys@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-black-keys">Black Keys</a>分享了 2024 年英国现场演出的详细信息，包括在伦敦布里克斯顿学院的演出。请在下面查找门票详细信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-black-keys-32-noel-gallagher-beck-tour-tickets-indie-sleaze-strokes-glastonbury-3431217">黑键乐队谈论重返英国和他们的“史诗”新专辑</a></strong></li></ul><p>巡演日期的消息是在乐队在一月份透露他们的新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-black-keys-new-single-beautiful-people-stay-high-and-announce-album-ohio-players-featuring-noel-gallagher-beck-3569722">“Ohio Players”</a>的细节之后发布的，他们与主打单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-black-keys-share-energetic-new-video-for-beautiful-people-stay-high-3575753">“Beautiful People (Stay High)”</a>一起分享了这张专辑。</p><p>这张专辑是 2022 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-black-keys-dropout-boogie-review-down-the-line-rock-destined-for-good-times-3223980">《Dropout Boogie》</a>的后续专辑，定于 4 月 5 日发行，随后将于今年春季晚些时候在英国举办三场演出。</p><p>三场演出中的第一场将于 4 月 27 日举行，开幕之夜将在曼彻斯特的新 Co-op Live 竞技场举行。此后，剩下的两晚将于 5 月 7 日和 5 月 8 日在布里克斯顿 O2 Academy 连续举行。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brixton-academy-announces-reopening-details-with-first-gig-3596293">今天早上（3 月 4 日）早些时候有消息称该场地将于 4 月重新开放，随后确认伦敦演出将在此</a>举办。布里克斯顿的 O2 学院于 2022 年 12 月关闭，此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/four-asake-fans-in-critical-condition-after-disturbance-at-brixton-academy-gig-3367923">Asake 音乐会上发生人群拥挤事件</a>，造成两人死亡。</p><p> Black Keys 演出门票将于当地时间本周五（3 月 8 日）上午 10 点开始发售，您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fthe-black-keys-tickets%2Fartist%2F847164" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>找到。<a href="https://theblackkeys.lnk.to/ohioplayers" target="_blank" rel="noopener">预订新专辑</a>的人还可以选择预售。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4FpcVHsJLU/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.8