tion-attachment-3370627" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3370627" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/brixton-academy-asake-getty-1.jpg" alt="布里克斯顿学院" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/brixton-academy-asake-getty-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/brixton-academy-asake-getty-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/brixton-academy-asake-getty-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/brixton-academy-asake-getty-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/brixton-academy-asake-getty-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/brixton-academy-asake-getty-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3370627" class="wp-caption-text"> 2022 年 12 月 15 日，Asake 演唱会发生人群拥挤事件后，警方在布里克斯顿 O2 学院拉起了警戒线。图片来源：Dan Kitwood/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>为了抵制关闭，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/petition-launched-to-save-brixton-academy-3436989">人们发起了网上请愿活动</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artists-and-industry-speak-out-to-save-brixton-academy-itd-be-a-tragedy-to-lose-such-an-iconic-venue-3437059">许多艺术家和行业专业人士也公开反对关闭该场馆的可能性</a>。</p><p> 2023 年 12 月，宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brixton-academy-allowed-to-retain-license-and-re-open-if-it-can-meet-robust-safety-rules-3498784">如果能够满足“严格”的安全规则，该场馆将被允许保留其许可证并重新开放</a>。这样做之后，今天早上分享了第一轮复出演出。</p><p> Nirvana UK（向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nirvana">Nirvana</a>致敬）和 The Smyths（向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smiths">The Smiths</a>致敬）将于 4 月 19 日星期五在场馆演出，随后的周五，Definitemightbe（向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a>致敬）和 UK Foo Fighters（向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foo-fighters">Foo Fighters</a>致敬） （4 月 26 日）。</p><p>除此之外，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/editors">编辑们</a>还宣布将于 5 月 2 日星期四在伦敦标志性场地举办一场演出。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-black-keys-announce-2024-uk-shows-including-brixton-academy-dates-buy-tickets-3596362">The Black Keys 宣布 2024 年英国演出（包括 Brixton Academy 演出日期）的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
