ixton-academy-reopening-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/brixton-academy-reopening-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>布里克斯顿学院宣布重新开放，并分享了自<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/four-asake-fans-in-critical-condition-after-disturbance-at-brixton-academy-gig-3367923">2022 年 12 月因人群拥挤</a>导致两人死亡而关闭以来的第一场演出的详细信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artists-and-industry-speak-out-to-save-brixton-academy-itd-be-a-tragedy-to-lose-such-an-iconic-venue-3437059"><b>艺术家和业界大声呼吁拯救布里克斯顿学院：“失去这样一个标志性的场地将是一场悲剧”</b></a></li></ul><p>自从<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/asake">Asake</a>音乐会上发生悲剧事件以来，O2 场馆已关闭，该事件导致<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tributes-paid-to-selfless-security-worker-killed-in-brixton-academy-asake-gig-crush-3370071">23 岁的 Gabrielle Hutchinson</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/woman-injured-during-asakes-o2-academy-brixton-show-dies-due-to-injuries-3368308">33 岁的 Rebecca Ikumelo</a>死亡。第三人情况危急。</p><p>自那时起，这座伦敦标志性场馆的未来就一直充满不确定性，直到去年 12 月宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brixton-academy-allowed-to-retain-license-and-re-open-if-it-can-meet-robust-safety-rules-3498784">，如果能够满足“严格”的安全规则，该场馆将被允许保留其许可证并重新开放</a>。请<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/these-are-the-77-robust-safety-conditions-brixton-academy-must-meet-for-re-opening-3502604">在此处查看已实施的 77 项措施的完整列表</a>。</p><p>布里克斯顿学院现已宣布下个月将举行一系列演出以纪念重新开放。</p><p> Nirvana UK（向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nirvana">Nirvana</a>致敬）和 The Smyths（向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smiths">The Smiths</a>致敬）将于 4 月 19 日星期五在场馆演出，随后的周五，Definitemightbe（向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a>致敬）和 UK Foo Fighters（向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foo-fighters">Foo Fighters</a>致敬） 4 月 26 日。本周五（3 月 8 日）上午 9 点（格林威治标准时间）演出门票从<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/o2-academy-brixton-tickets-london/venue/507981?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=WVMWLAT55xyPTjiVXp0rVUKSUkH3PuSZnRXHRo0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>开始发售。预售也将于周三（3 月 6 日）上午 10 点（格林威治标准时间）开始。</p><p>除此之外，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/editors">编辑们</a>还宣布将于 5 月 2 日星期四在伦敦标志性场地举办一场演出， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/THE-BLACK-KEYS">The Black Keys</a>将于 5 月 7 日星期二和 5 月 8 日星期三进行两晚的驻场演出。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="zxx" dir="ltr"> <a href="https://t.co/9TDQb18v8w">pic.twitter.com/9TDQb18v8w</a></p><p> — O2 布里克斯顿学院 (@O2AcademyBrix) <a href="https://twitter.com/O2AcademyBrix/status/1764582530030719013?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 3 月 4 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4FpPCIC7xJ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https:/